title: Brood of the Dark Moon
creator: Charles W. Diffin
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
description: LibriVox recording of Brood of the Dark Moon, by Charles W. Diffin. Read by Richard Kilmer. Once more Chet, Walt and Diane are united in a wild ride to the Dark Moon—but this time they go as prisoners of their deadly enemy Schwartzmann.(Summary by Charles Diffin) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
